data.revised_prompt: A detailed painting depicting the skyline of Seattle, imitating the style of the post-impressionist artist Van Gogh, notable for his bold, dramatic brushstrokes and emotive use of color. The painting showcases key landmarks of Seattle like the Space Needle and the skyscrapers with vivid colors and swirling skies, capturing vibrant blue and gold tones. The painting is in oil medium, like the works of Van Gogh, with the swirling strokes giving a sense of movement and energy.
